{"lemma":"صَنْدَلِ","slug":"صَنْدَلِ","root":"ص.ن.د.ل","root_slug":"ص-ن-د-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ن-د-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n24990","n24992"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%8E%D9%86%D9%92%D8%AF%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sandalwood"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sandals"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"barge, lighter, freight barge, sandal"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Middle Persian cndl (čandal), likely from Gandhari 𐨕𐨎𐨡𐨣 (caṃdana), from Sanskrit चन्दन (candana).\n\nA vessel already known to the Ṭūlūnids from Byzantine Greek σανδάλιον (sandálion) having both the ship and the shoe sense, diminutive of σάνδαλον (sándalon)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n24990","headword_ar":"صَنْدَلَ","root":"Sndl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", said of a camel, (IAar, M, O, K,) and of an ass, (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was big in the head,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, M, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and hard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hardy, and large."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["IAar","M","O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n24992","headword_ar":"صَنْدَلٌ","root":"Sndl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", applied to an ass, (T, TA,) or to a camel, (S, O,) or to both, as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SunaAdilN","text_ar":"صُنَادِلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Big in the head:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strong in make, big in the head:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"large, strong, big in the head:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"big in the head, and hard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hardy, and large:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or accord. to IDrd, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SunaAdilN","text_ar":"صُنَادِلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", applied to a camel, signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strong,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hardy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O:) the pl! of the former [or of each] is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SanaAdila","text_ar":"صَنَادِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O.)       -A2-  Also, i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SanodalN","text_ar":"صَنْدَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A species of trees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a kind of wood,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"well known,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of sweet odour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and of several sorts;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sandal-wood;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the best of which is the red,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the white,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the yellow;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a discutient of tumours, beneficial as a remedy for palpitation and for the headache and for weakness of the hot stomach and for fevers:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the infusion of its sawdust and the continual smelling of it weaken the venereal faculty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A3-  It is also a Pers. word ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kalimapN A^aEojamiy~apN","text_ar":"كَلِمَةٌ اَعْجَمِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or rather an arabicized word from the Pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sanodal","text_ar":"سَنْدَل"},{"kind":"text","text":"]) signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing resembling the boot"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxuf~","text_ar":"الخُفّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the sole of which are nails:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SanaAdilu","text_ar":"صَنَادِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["T","TA","S","O","M","K","Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}